******************************************
setpen	-	help file for setpen macro
******************************************

FORMAT:		setpen(<arg1>,<arg2>)

arg1 - maxpen
arg2 - maximum number of pens to be used
       (must be between 1 and maxpen)


This macro allows the user to interactively define
at the time of changing the plotter (to an HP) the
maximum number of pens to be used by the HP plotter.
